description: Welcome to 184 Tudor Street! Nestled on a quiet South Boston street, this beautifully renovated single-family home blends modern luxury with classic charm. The main level features a stunning chef’s kitchen with top-of-the-line appliances, seamlessly flowing into a spacious, open living room—perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. Upstairs, exposed brick accents lead you to two generously sized guest bedrooms and a stylish full bathroom. The third floor is dedicated to a sweeping primary suite, complete with a skylit walk-in closet and a spa-like en-suite bathroom designed for ultimate relaxation. The lower level offers flexible space ideal for a home office, gym, or media room, along with an additional full bathroom showcasing elegant tile finishes. To top it off, this home includes two coveted off-street parking spots. Don’t miss the chance to make this exceptional property your own.
